{"tid":816913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=搾汁  男工遭碎冰機夾3指濺血","createTime":"2018-09-13T04:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T05:41:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05567bc0a5d370ef56eb2da1b9d33584fd774155","tid":816913,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"將軍澳翠林邨翠林新城發生工業意外。今日(13日)凌晨零時許，一名姓梁(46歲)工人在上址街市工作，操作一部碎冰機時，右手掌意外被夾着，動彈不得，痛得大叫，工友上前施援，無法將其手拉出，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防員用工具撬開機器，成功為工人解困，證實3隻手指被夾傷，包括中指、無名指及尾指，鮮血淋漓，由救護車直送往伊利沙伯醫院救治，暫未知有否骨折。警方封鎖現場調查後，列作工業意外處理，稍後聯絡相關部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180913/bkn-20180913011158720-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180913%2Fbkn-20180913011158720-0913_00822_001.html&d=1omiQOYDo2tM%2Bh4nfUKcwp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=25c7844a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180913/bkn-20180913011158720-0913_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"76afce7931925ae3c86241983b269137b583e914","tid":816913,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f9e0a64784924b573652bf0ef59215960793fd","tid":816913,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/125837_3e9dc0c5697d627ce272520103dea663.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F125837_3e9dc0c5697d627ce272520103dea663.gif&h=bc6efdbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb341f74ecb0c44daadb419aa9598fffa88eea47","tid":816913,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f9e0a64784924b573652bf0ef59215960793fd","tid":81691